---
layout: layouts/story.njk
title: Ferni - Your AI Life Coach
description: Six AI specialists who actually listen, remember everything, and help you grow. Available 24/7 by voice or text.
---

{# ============================================
   NAVIGATION
   ============================================ #}
<nav class="nav" id="nav">
  <div class="nav__inner">
    <a href="/" class="nav__logo">
      <span class="nav__logo-mark">FN</span>
      Ferni
    </a>
    
    <ul class="nav__links">
      <li><a href="#team" class="nav__link">Team</a></li>
      <li><a href="#how-it-works" class="nav__link">How It Works</a></li>
      <li><a href="#pricing" class="nav__link">Pricing</a></li>
      <li><a href="#faq" class="nav__link">FAQ</a></li>
    </ul>
    
    <a href="{{ site.appUrl }}" class="nav__cta">Get Started</a>
  </div>
</nav>

{# ============================================
   SECTION 1: HERO
   "Better than human" - The hook
   ============================================ #}
<section class="section section--hero" id="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero__content">
      <p class="hero__eyebrow">Your AI Life Coach</p>
      
      <h1 class="hero__headline">
        {{ site.hero.headline }}
        <span class="hero__headline-accent">{{ site.hero.headlineAccent }}</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="hero__subhead">
        Six AI specialists who actually listen, remember everything, and help you grow. Available 24/7 by voice or text.
      </p>
      
      <div class="hero__cta">
        <a href="{{ site.hero.cta.primary.url }}" class="btn btn--primary">
          Get started free
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="tel:{{ site.phoneRaw }}" class="btn btn--secondary">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
          </svg>
          {{ site.phone }}
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="hero__trust">
        <span><strong>10K+</strong> conversations</span>
        <span class="hero__trust-divider">•</span>
        <span><strong>&lt;500ms</strong> response</span>
        <span class="hero__trust-divider">•</span>
        <span><strong>∞</strong> memory</span>
      </div>
      
      {# Interactive Demo #}
      <div class="hero__demo">
        <div class="hero__input-wrapper">
          <input 
            type="text" 
            class="hero__input"
            placeholder="What's on your mind?"
            autocomplete="off"
          >
          <button class="hero__mic-btn" aria-label="Voice input">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v7a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3Z"/>
              <path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/>
              <line x1="12" x2="12" y1="19" y2="22"/>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="hero__prompts">
          <button class="hero__prompt">Feeling overwhelmed</button>
          <button class="hero__prompt">Build better habits</button>
          <button class="hero__prompt">Big decision</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="hero__scroll" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="hero__scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ============================================
   SECTION 2: THE PROMISE
   "Finally, someone who actually listens"
   ============================================ #}
<section class="section section--alt" id="promise">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="promise reveal">
      <p class="promise__quote">
        "We exist in the space between—the <span class="promise__quote-accent">2am worry</span>, 
        the commute contemplation, the moment before a big decision. We're not replacing 
        human connection; we're <span class="promise__quote-accent">filling the gaps</span> 
        when your people aren't available."
      </p>
      <p class="promise__description">
        Ferni is the AI that actually listens. Warm like a trusted friend, grounded and calm, 
        wise without judgment, fully present, and genuinely human.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ============================================
   SECTION 3: MEET THE TEAM
   Six AI specialists
   ============================================ #}
<section class="section" id="team">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__header reveal">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Meet Your Team</p>
      <h2 class="section__title">Six specialists.<br>One conversation.</h2>
      <p class="section__subtitle">
        Each brings unique expertise. Ferni coordinates them seamlessly based on what you need.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="team-grid reveal-stagger">
      {% for member in site.team %}
      <div class="team-card">
        <div class="team-card__avatar" style="background: {{ member.color }};">
          {{ member.initials }}
        </div>
        <h3 class="team-card__name">{{ member.name }}</h3>
        <p class="team-card__role">{{ member.role }}</p>
        <p class="team-card__bio">{{ member.bio }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ============================================
   SECTION 4: HOW IT WORKS
   Voice, Memory, 24/7
   ============================================ #}
<section class="section section--alt" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__header reveal">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">How It Works</p>
      <h2 class="section__title">As easy as calling a friend</h2>
      <p class="section__subtitle">
        No app required. Just call, text, or use the web app. We handle the rest.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="features-grid reveal-stagger">
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v7a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3Z"/>
            <path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/>
            <line x1="12" x2="12" y1="19" y2="22"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature__title">Voice-First</h3>
        <p class="feature__description">
          Call {{ site.phone }} from any phone. No download, no login. Just talk naturally like you would with a friend.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature__title">Infinite Memory</h3>
        <p class="feature__description">
          Ferni remembers every conversation. Your context, your goals, your story—all saved and used to help you better.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature__title">Always Available</h3>
        <p class="feature__description">
          24/7, 365 days a year. Whether it's 2am anxiety or a lunch break check-in, Ferni is there when you need support.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ============================================
   SECTION 5: TESTIMONIALS
   Social proof
   ============================================ #}
<section class="section" id="testimonials">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__header reveal">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Loved By</p>
      <h2 class="section__title">People like you</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="testimonials-grid reveal-stagger">
      {% for testimonial in site.testimonials %}
      <div class="testimonial{% if testimonial.featured %} testimonial--featured{% endif %}">
        <p class="testimonial__quote">"{{ testimonial.quote }}"</p>
        <div class="testimonial__author">
          <div class="testimonial__avatar">{{ testimonial.initials }}</div>
          <div>
            <p class="testimonial__name">{{ testimonial.author }}</p>
            <p class="testimonial__role">{{ testimonial.role }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

